職能治療研究方法導論                    


  	The concept of research is gaining more and more attention nowadays. Research provides important evidence to guide clinical practice (evidence-based practice) and to direct the development of knowledge. This course introduces basic components of research, including quantitative and qualitative research models, literature search, research designs and methodology. In addition, this course will go over concepts regarding abilities needed to have for being a consumer of research, such as locating the literature, evaluating evidence, and synthesizing research. Moreover, in view of the trend of e-learning, this course will incorporate “i-teach” course platform and students are encouraged to download course materials, hand in assignments, exchange ideas through this platform. Upon finishing the course, students will be able to read and understand journal articles and to evaluate the research reports.

課程教育目標 

C. 培育具有主動求知、終身學習及貢獻科學研究之發展的職能治療人才 
課程基本素養與核心能力 

[核心能力]獨立思考及問題解決之能力
培養具有獨立思考、臨床推理及問題解決的能力，並能終身學習。創新與領導能力
培養具有創新與領導的能力，以為專業技能或研究奠基。 
